  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math><mn>5</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn></math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math><mn>15</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>24</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>27</mn></math></p>\n<p>For each real number <math><mi>r</mi></math>, which of the following points lies on the graph of each equation in the <em>xy</em>-plane for the given system?</p>",
