  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. The second equation is three times the first, so both represent the same line. Solving 5x + 8y = 9 for y: y = (9 - 5x)/8. Setting x = r gives the point (r, (9 - 5r)/8). The other choices use incorrect rearrangements.</p>",
